  "Description": {
    "English": "A pane of watchful <span class=\"name name-special\">g l a s s</span>, retrieved from the smoking remains of the corrupted swarm's <span class=\"name name-technology\">Dissonance Resonators</span>. It emits more light than it reflects, casting a faint purple hue on its surroundings.<br><br>Highly sought after for salvage operations, as it can be used to bypass the security systems of key <span class=\"name name-technology\">Sentinel ship technologies</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一面永远凝视着的<span class=\"name name-special\">玻璃</span>，来源于腐化群集浓烟滚滚的残骸中的<span class=\"name name-technology\">不谐共振器</span>。玻璃施放着超出反射量的光芒，因此位于其周遭的一切都被染上了淡淡的紫色。<br><br>此物是各类回收作业人心目中的抢手货，因为它能够被用于破解关键<span class=\"name name-technology\">护卫飞船技术</span>的安全系统。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一片警惕戒備的<span class=\"name name-special\">玻 璃</span>，從受腐蝕機群的<span class=\"name name-technology\">不和諧共振器</span>冒煙殘骸中回收而來。這片玻璃散發的光遠比反射還多，在周圍灑落微弱的紫色光芒。<br><br>因為可以用來繞過關鍵<span class=\"name name-technology\">巡警太空船科技</span>的保全系統，在回收行動中廣受歡迎。"
  },
