    "SimplifiedChinese": "从腐化群集的<span class=\"name name-technology\">不谐共振器</span>收获<span class=\"name name-special\">反转镜面</span>。<br>于存在腐化护卫的世界使用分析面甲（<span class=\"name name-img\">AIM</span>）寻找这些可憎的机器。",
